      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nJust following up on my previous note – many product leaders see a 30% reduction in time‑to‑insight when pairing InsightX with our real‑time analytics engine. I’d love to share a short demo tailored to Acme’s use case.\n\nThanks,\n[Your Name]"
    },
    {
      "step": 3,
      "subject": "Case study: Scaling product analytics for fast‑growing SaaS firms",
      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nI thought you might find this case study useful – a SaaS company similar to Acme saw a 45% increase in product adoption after integrating our solution with their analytics stack. Happy to discuss how this could apply to InsightX.\n\nRegards,\n[Your Name]"
